{
  "sn6.9:0.1": "Saṁyutta Nikāya 6.9 ",
  "sn6.9:0.2": "1. Paṭhamavagga ",
  "sn6.9:0.3": "Turūbrahmasutta ",
  "sn6.9:1.1": "Sāvatthinidānaṁ. ",
  "sn6.9:1.2": "Tena kho pana samayena kokāliko bhikkhu ābādhiko hoti dukkhito bāḷhagilāno. ",
  "sn6.9:1.3": "Atha kho turū paccekabrahmā abhikkantāya rattiyā abhikkantavaṇṇo kevalakappaṁ jetavanaṁ obhāsetvā yena kokāliko bhikkhu tenupasaṅkami; upasaṅkamitvā vehāsaṁ ṭhito kokālikaṁ bhikkhuṁ etadavoca: ",
  "sn6.9:1.4": "“pasādehi, kokālika, sāriputtamoggallānesu cittaṁ. ",
  "sn6.9:1.5": "Pesalā sāriputtamoggallānā”ti. ",
  "sn6.9:1.6": "“Kosi tvaṁ, āvuso”ti? ",
  "sn6.9:1.7": "“Ahaṁ turū paccekabrahmā”ti. ",
  "sn6.9:1.8": "“Nanu tvaṁ, āvuso, bhagavatā anāgāmī byākato, atha kiñcarahi idhāgato? ",
  "sn6.9:1.9": "Passa, yāvañca te idaṁ aparaddhan”ti. ",
  "sn6.9:2.1": "“Purisassa hi jātassa, ",
  "sn6.9:2.2": "kuṭhārī jāyate mukhe; ",
  "sn6.9:2.3": "Yāya chindati attānaṁ, ",
  "sn6.9:2.4": "bālo dubbhāsitaṁ bhaṇaṁ. ",
  "sn6.9:3.1": "Yo nindiyaṁ pasaṁsati, ",
  "sn6.9:3.2": "Taṁ vā nindati yo pasaṁsiyo; ",
  "sn6.9:3.3": "Vicināti mukhena so kaliṁ, ",
  "sn6.9:3.4": "Kalinā tena sukhaṁ na vindati. ",
  "sn6.9:4.1": "Appamattako ayaṁ kali, ",
  "sn6.9:4.2": "Yo akkhesu dhanaparājayo; ",
  "sn6.9:4.3": "Sabbassāpi sahāpi attanā, ",
  "sn6.9:4.4": "Ayameva mahantataro kali; ",
  "sn6.9:4.5": "Yo sugatesu manaṁ padosaye. ",
  "sn6.9:5.1": "Sataṁ sahassānaṁ nirabbudānaṁ, ",
  "sn6.9:5.2": "Chattiṁsati pañca ca abbudāni; ",
  "sn6.9:5.3": "Yamariyagarahī nirayaṁ upeti, ",
  "sn6.9:5.4": "Vācaṁ manañca paṇidhāya pāpakan”ti. "
}